        <p>2018/19 - <strong>4th Place</strong> - Div 1 Surrey Volleyball League</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-us-card">
        <h1>Training and Matches</h1>
        <p>Please visit the <%= link_to 'Venues', venues_path, class: "menu-item" %> page for more details on training times and sports halls locations</p>
      </div>
